Package app.controller.user

Class ActionResult

java.lang.Object
app.controller.user.ActionResult
public class ActionResult extends Object
The ActionResult class encapsulates the result of a user-related action, such as a login attempt. It holds a boolean result indicating the success or failure of the action and an integer representing the user type.

This class provides getters and setters for accessing and modifying these properties.
